        <item>
            <title>3.7.4</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 16:55:08 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>126</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.7.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 3.7.4</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>AI Rename now retries suggestions that match the current file name</li><li>Reanalyze unchanged or failed files together with one click</li><li>Scanned PDFs keep more visual context for better name suggestions</li><li>Clearer guidance when macOS Keychain prevents cloud AI from working</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>Batch errors are easier to read and whole-batch failures now show an alert</li></ul>
]]></description>
